      • load

        public void load()
          throws FindException
        Description copied from interface: Entity

        Causes this instance to load its data by contacting the remote service and requesting information. Once loaded, subsequent calls to this method have no effect.

        This method is useful for proxy entities found at the edge of the graph.

        Specified by:
        load in interface Entity
        Specified by:
        load in class EntityProxy
        Throws:
        FindException - If the lookup fails before it is able to generate a Response object.
        See Also:
        Entity.isProxy(), Entity.isLoaded(), EntityProxy
